ing":"Find help while inside Source Linker","search.sourceLinker.tutorial.slideOneAlt":"Sources being attached to a family tree.","search.sourceLinker.tutorial.slideOneContent":"We needed to replace the old version because it used outdated technology. <strong>There are also a few design changes to make it easier to link sources to your ancestors.</strong><br/><br/> This overview will show you the most important changes.","search.sourceLinker.tutorial.slideOneHeading":"Welcome to the new Source Linker!","search.sourceLinker.tutorial.slideThreeAlt":"Inaccurate tree data being corrected.","search.sourceLinker.tutorial.slideThreeContent":"Now you can edit information in Family Tree without leaving Source Linker. To edit, find facts in the right column labeled <strong>Different</strong> and click the <strong>pencil icon</strong>. Clicking the pencil allows you to correct inaccuracies and add more details to Family Tree.","search.sourceLinker.tutorial.slideThreeContent.CET":"Now you can edit information in {treeName} without leaving Source Linker. To edit, find facts in the right column labeled <strong>Different</strong> and click the <strong>pencil icon</strong>. Clicking the pencil allows you to correct inaccuracies and add more details to {treeName}.","search.sourceLinker.tutorial.slideThreeHeading":"Edit Family Tree facts while in Source Linker","search.sourceLinker.tutorial.slideThreeHeading.CET":"Edit {treeName} facts while in Source Linker","search.sourceLinker.tutorial.slideTwoAlt":"Clicking attach button on a selected tree person.","search.sourceLinker.tutorial.slideTwoContent":"We\u2019ve updated our technology to provide a faster, more secure experience. It\u2019s the same Source Linker but with some important additions!","search.sourceLinker.tutorial.slideTwoHeading":"A new look with a familiar feel","search.sourceLinker.tutorial.tipsAndResources":"Tips and Resources","search.sourceLinker.tutorial.title":"Learn More About Source Linker","search.sourceLinker.tu