cess":"This item is not currently digitally accessible due to access restrictions.","search.cat.details.restricted.regPat":"This item is viewable by registered users.","search.cat.details.seriesLabel":"Series","search.cat.details.statement_responsibility":"Statement of Responsibility","search.cat.details.subjects":"Subjects","search.cat.details.summary_contents":"Summary Contents","search.cat.details.surnameSubjects":"Surname Subjects","search.cat.detailsTitle":"FamilySearch Catalog: {displayTitle}","search.cat.familySearchCatalog":"FamilySearch Catalog","search.cat.familySearchLibrary.button":"Browse the Library Catalog","search.cat.familySearchLibrary.description":"The FamilySearch Library Catalog lists physical items available at the Library, as well as links to items in the FamilySearch Digital Library. Search for books, microfilms, microfiche, maps, and more, and browse curated lists to aid in your research.","search.cat.familySearchLibrary.image.alt":"FamilySearch Library","search.cat.familySearchLibrary.title":"FamilySearch Library Catalog","search.cat.helpArticleLink":"Learn How to Use the Catalog","search.cat.helpArticleLink.seeTipsAndResources":"See Tips and Resources","search.cat.metaDescription":"Access the world\u2019s largest collection of genealogy resources with the FamilySearch Catalog. Find birth certificates, maps, periodicals, and more.","search.cat.print.addTitles":"1. Add titles to your list","search.cat.print.addTitlesInstruction":"Click <bolded>Add</bolded> on any title to add it to your print list.","search.cat.print.authorHead":"Author","search.cat.print.back":"Back","search.cat.print.callNumberHead":"Call Number","search.cat.print.columnHeader":"Remove Button","search.cat.print.emptyList":"Your catalog print list is empty","search.cat.print.errorMessage":"Unfortunately, there was an error getting one or more of your print list items. Try refreshing the page, or come back later.","search.cat.print.getStarted":"Get started in the catalog","search.cat.print.getStartedInstruction":"Head over to the catalog to start researching in books, microfilm, microfiche, and publications available from Family Search","search.cat.print.goToCatalog":"Go to the catalog","search.cat.print.listDescription":"The catalog print list helps you gather and print Family Search resources relevant to your search","search.cat.print.mobileHeadings":"Title, Author, Call Number","search.cat.print.pageTitle":"Catalog Print List","search.cat.print.printAction":"Print","search.cat.print.printList":"2. Print your list","search.cat.print.printListHeader":"Catalog Print List ({printListLength})","search.cat.print.printListInstruction":"When done adding, click on the <FirstBolded>Catalog Print List</FirstBolded> in the top right, then click the blue <SecondBolded>Print</SecondBolded> button.","search.cat.print.removeAll":"Remove all from list","search.cat.print.removeItem":"Remove","search.cat.print.startResearch":"3. Start your research","search.cat.print.startResearchInstruction":"Check off titles after looking for your ancestors within them.","search.cat.print.titleHead":"Title","search.cat.resultsTitle":"Catalog Search Results for {parameters}","search.cat.searchLandingTitle":"Explore FamilySearch Catalog to Find Genealogy Resources","search.cat.socialShareDescription":"Access the world\u2019s largest collection of genealogy resources with the FamilySearch Catalog.","search.cat.socialShareTitle":"Search the FamilySearch Catalog","search.cat.subheader2":"Find books, records, images, and other important resources offered through the FamilySearch website, the FamilySearch Library, and select FamilySearch Centers around the world.","search.cat.visitLibrary":"Planning a visit to the FamilySearch Library in Salt Lake City, Utah? Start here.","search.catalog.results.placeFilters.currentPlace":"See: places within {currentPlace}","search.catalog.results.placeFilters.currentPlace.tooltip":"Display places within {currentPlace} to narrow the search","search.catalog.results.placeFilters.parentPlace":"See: part of {parentPlace}","search.catalog.results.placeFilters.parentPlace.tooltip":"Search for {parentPlace}","search.catalog.results.placeNotes":"Notes","search.catalog.results.placeNotes.link":"Place Information","search.catalog.results.placeNotesAria":"Place Notes","search.catalog.results.placeOverlayTitle":"Places within {shortCurrentPlace}","search.catalog.tutorial.description":"Learn more about this tool and how to use it effectively.","search.catalog.tutorial.endSlideAlt":"An illustration of a woman looking a computer shows that that she wants to learn more about the FamilySearch Catalog.","search.catalog.tutorial.endSlideLearnMore":"Learn More","search.catalog.tutorial.endSlideParagraphOne":"We\u2019re always trying to improve. If you have a suggestion, click the <strong>Feedback Button</strong> and share it with us!","search.catalog.tutorial.endSlideParagraphTwo":"Want to learn more tips about how to use the FamilySearch Catalog? Click the button below to visit the FamilySearch Catalog hub page.","search.catalog.tutorial.slideFourAlt":"A simplified image of the FamilySearch Catalog search results page shows where place filters are located.","search.catalog.tutorial.slideFourBulletPointOne":"The FamilySearch Catalog now uses the same, growing list of standard places as the rest of our site. As our collection grows, so does your ability to find the items you need within it. You can expand and narrow places with filters at the top of the screen.","search.catalog.tutorial.slideFourHeading":"Enhanced Places","search.catalog.tutorial.slideOneAlt":"A simplified image of the FamilySearch Catalog search page shows how the user interface changed.","search.catalog.tutorial.slideOneContent.bulletPoint1":"The catalog has used the same technology for over 15 years.","search.catalog.tutorial.slideOneContent.bulletPoint2":"This older technology served us well but is no longer supportable. To keep the catalog online and allow its content to grow with our collection, we had to upgrade to new technology.","search.catalog.tutorial.slideOneHeading":"Why did the catalog change?","search.catalog.tutorial.slideThreeAlt":"File folders being put into a single place illustrates that the data in the FamilySearch Catalog is being updated.","search.catalog.tutorial.slideThreeContent":"In 2022, we had to stop adding new holdings to the old catalog. We\'ve added the backlog to the new catalog and add new holdings as they are acquired.","search.catalog.tutorial.slideThreeHeading":"Improved Data","search.catalog.tutorial.slideTwoAlt":"A simplified illustration of the FamilySearch Catalog search results page shows where the filters are located.","search.catalog.tutorial.slideTwoContent.bulletPoint1":"Where possible, the catalog works exactly like it did before.","search.catalog.tutorial.slideTwoContent.bulletPoint2":"You can still make searches, change your search to be broader or narrower, find items in the FamilySearch collection (where they are located, and whether they are available online), and create print lists.","search.catalog.tutorial.slideTwoHeading":"New technology. Same features.","search.catalog.tutorial.title":"Learn More About Catalog","search.cms-collections.collection-header.images":"{count, plural, one {# Image} other {# Images}}","search.cms-collections.collection-header.personas":"{count, plural, one {# Persona} other {# Personas}}","search.cms-collections.collection-header.record-type-with-types":"{count, plural, one {Record Type: {types}} other {Record Types: {types}}}","search.cms-collections.collection-header.records":"{count, plural, one {# Record} other {# Records}}","search.cms-collections.last-modified.label":"Last Modified","search.cms-collections.leaving-fs.description.info":"Clicking \'Go to {provider}\' will take you outside FamilySearch.org.","search.cms-collections.leaving-fs.description.paid":"Fees and other terms may apply.","search.cms-collections.leaving-fs.description.partner-access":"FamilySearch provides free access to some partner sites. <learnMoreLink>Learn more</learnMoreLink>","search.cms-collections.leaving-fs.go-to-provider":"Go to {provider}","search.cms-collections.leaving-fs.heading":"Leaving FamilySearch","search.cms-collections.leaving-fs.stay":"Stay","search.cms-collections.no-citation":"No citation information available for this collection.","search.cms-collections.related-collections.heading":"Related Collections","search.cms-collections.related-resources.error":"Unable to load resources at this time.","search.cms-collections.related-resources.external-heading":"Internet Collections","search.cms-collections.related-resources.internal-heading":"Collections from FamilySearch","search.cms-collections.related-resources.no-results":"No related resources found.","search.cms-collections.related-resources.untitled":"Untitled Collection","search.cms-collections.related-resources.view-all":"View All","search.cms-collections.source-information.heading":"Source information","search.cms-collections.source-information.language":"Language","search.cms-collections.source-information.location-of-original-records":"Location of Original Records","search.cms-collections.start-your-search.heading":"Start your search","search.collection.details.browseAllImages":"Browse All {imageCount} Images","search.collection.details.browseWiki":"Browse the Wiki","search.collection.details.citeThisCollection":"Cite This Collection","search.collection.details.copiedCitation":"Copied Citation to Clipboard","search.collection.details.copyCitation":"Copy Citation","search.collection.details.copyRecordError":"Something went wrong. Try again later.","search.collection.details.howToUse":"How to Use This Collection","search.collection.form.select.item.action":"Select Item","search.collection.list.page.description":"Search and explore over 2,000 historical record collections between 655 A.D. and today, gathered from around the world.  Find your ancestors and add them to your family tree.","search.collection.list.page.title":"Historical Record Collections","search.collections.allRegionText":"All {regionName}","search.collections.autoUpdateLabel":"Enter a collection title in the search field. Results will filter as you type.","search.collections.browseImages":"Browse Images","search.collections.collectionTitle":"Collection Title","search.collections.collectionTitle.placeholder":"Enter a collection title","search.collections.dismissChipLabel":"Dismiss {chipName}","search.collections.docCameraIconToolTip":"These images were captured by another organization and are available to view outside FamilySearch.","search.collections.filterCollections":"Filter Collections","search.collections.filters":"Filters ({filterCount, number})","search.collections.filters.numberOfResults":"Filtered Results ({resultCount, number})","search.collections.imageAvailability":"Image Availability","search.collections.lastUpdated":"Last Updated","search.collections.mediaCameraIconToolTip":"These images are available to view on FamilySearch.","search.collections.mobileColumnHeader":"Collection Title, Records, Last Updated","search.collections.numberOfResults":"Results ({resultCount, number})","search.collections.records":"Records","search.collections.recordsUpdate":"Records & Last Updated","search.darkMode":"Dark Mode","search.darkMode.button":"Dark Mode Button","search.disclaimerDialog.dismiss":"Dismiss","search.disclaimerDialog.doNotShowAgain":"Don\'t Show This Again","search.disclaimerDialog.legalNotice":"Legal Notice","search.error.header":"Something Went Wrong","search.error.imageAlt":"Something Went Wrong","search.error.noResults.header":"No Results Found","search.error.noResults.imageAlt":"No Results","search.fhcBanner.download":"Download","search.fhcBanner.messageRebranded":"Many limited-access records are available in FamilySearch centers. If you are currently in a FamilySearch center, download the browser extension to get access.","search.film-viewer.full-text-search.available-in-fts.icon-button.title":"This film is available in Full-Text Search","search.film-viewer.full-text-search.not-available-in-fts.icon-button.title":"This film is not available in Full-Text Search","search.film-viewer.keyboard-shortcuts.left-and-right-arrows":"Left & Right Arrows","search.filmViewer.attachImageToTree":"Attach image to tree","search.filmViewer.attachImageToTree.description":"Attach Image to Tree","search.filmViewer.attachImageToTree.disabledDescription":"To attach, go to the Image Index tab at the bottom","search.filmViewer.attachToTree":"Attach to Tree","search.filmViewer.attachToTree.overlayMessage":"You must sign in to FamilySearch to access your sources.","search.filmViewer.bottomSheet.attach-person-aria-label":"Attach {personName} to Family Tree","search.filmViewer.bottomSheet.attach-person-to-tree.button":"Attach","search.filmViewer.bottomSheet.catalogRecord.heading":"Catalog Record","search.filmViewer.bottomSheet.citation.heading":"Citation","search.filmViewer.bottomSheet.citationCopiedToClipboard":"Citation copied to clipboard.","search.filmViewer.bottomSheet.copyCitation.button":"Copy Citation","search.filmViewer.bottomSheet.emptyCatalogRows":"No catalog records are available.","search.filmViewer.bottomSheet.emptyCitation":"No citation is available.","search.filmViewer.bottomSheet.failedToCopyCitationCopiedToClipboard":"Failed to copy citation to clipboard.","search.filmViewer.bottomSheet.filmNote.heading":"Film/Digital Note","search.filmViewer.bottomSheet.imageIndex.tab":"Image Index","search.filmViewer.bottomSheet.information.tab":"Information","search.filmViewer.bottomSheet.itemNumber.heading":"Item Number","search.filmViewer.bottomSheet.view-record-aria-label":"View record for {personName}","search.filmViewer.filmNumber":"Film # {filmNumber}","search.filmViewer.keyboard-shortcuts.increase-and-decrease-brightness":"Increase/Decrease Brightness","search.filmViewer.keyboard-shortcuts.increase-decrease-contrast":"Increase/Decrease Contrast","search.filmViewer.keyboard-shortcuts.invert-image-colors":"Invert Image Colors","search.filmViewer.keyboard-shortcuts.pan-image":"Pan Image Up/Down/Left/Right","search.filmViewer.keyboard-shortcuts.pan-image-left-right":"Pan Image Left/Right","search.filmViewer.keyboard-shortcuts.pan-image-up-down":"Pan Image Up/Down","search.filmViewer.keyboard-shortcuts.previous-and-next-image":"Previous/Next Image","search.filmViewer.keyboard-shortcuts.rotate-image-right":"Rotate Image Right","search.filmViewer.noImageIndexes":"No indexes are available for this image.","search.filmViewer.resetSortOrder":"Reset to Original Sort Order","search.filmViewer.viewedImage":"Image has previously been viewed","search.filmViewer.whatIsNew.description":"We regularly update our image viewer to stay current with new technology. Explore the new features and enjoy an improved experience!","search.filmViewer.whatIsNew.keyboardShortcutTable.action.heading":"Action","search.filmViewer.whatIsNew.keyboardShortcutTable.description":"Use these simple shortcuts on your keyboard to improve and enhance how you view images.","search.filmViewer.whatIsNew.keyboardShortcutTable.heading":"Introducing Keyboard Shortcuts","search.filmViewer.whatIsNew.keyboardShortcutTable.note":"To explore the entire list of shortcuts, see <Link>New Keyboard Shortcuts</Link>.","search.filmViewer.whatIsNew.keyboardShortcutTable.shortcut.heading":"Shortcut","search.filmViewer.whatIsNew.title":"We\'ve Updated a Few Things","search.filter.tutorial.startTourOverlay.description1":"We\'ve made some updates to our search experience, including new filters for narrowing your search results.","search.filter.tutorial.startTourOverlay.description2":"Take a quick tour to see what\'s changed and how it can help you find the records you care about.","search.filter.tutorial.startTourOverlay.startTourButton":"Start Tour","search.filter.tutorial.startTourOverlay.title":"Finding records just got easier","search.filter.tutorial.title":"Filtering Tutorial","search.filtering.tutStepFiveDesc":"Active filters appear at the top of the search pane. Click the <strong>X</strong> to remove one\u2014or click <strong>Clear Filters</strong> to start fresh.","search.filtering.tutStepFiveTitle":"Clearing your filters","search.filtering.tutStepFourDesc":"Checkbox filters let you select more than one option. Filters with a down arrow open to show more specific choices.<br><br> The Year and Place filters allow you to select multiple places at the same level, or click the down arrow to view more specific dates or locations.","search.filtering.tutStepFourTitle":"Applying your filters","search.filtering.tutStepOneDesc":"Everything you need to edit your search and view your results is now on the left side of the screen.","search.filtering.tutStepOneTitle":"New layout, upgraded tools","search.filtering.tutStepSixDesc":"You\u2019re ready to start using the new search filters. If you have thoughts or suggestions, click the Feedback button to let us know.","search.filtering.tutStepSixTitle":"You\u2019re all set!","search.filtering.tutStepThreeDesc":"Use filters to narrow your search. Click <strong>Apply</strong> each time you are ready to add or change your filter(s).","search.filtering.tutStepThreeTitle":"Narrowing your search","search.filtering.tutStepTwoDesc":"Click <strong>Edit Search</strong> to modify your search. This opens the full form\u2014perfect for tweaking details or starting fresh.","search.filtering.tutStepTwoTitle":"Edit your search","search.filters.showAllNum":"Show All {count}","search.filters.tutorial.alert":"<Link>Learn how</Link> the updated search filters can improve your search.","search.full-text.collection.title":"Full-Text: Collection Details","search.full-text.metaDescription":"Search for your ancestors in birth certificates, marriage registrations, census records, and other documents.","search.full-text.results":"Full-Text Search Results","search.full.text.search.collection.description.autocollection":"Note: This is a dynamic, computer-generated collection. As the collection\'s contents grow, the collection title, descriptive data, and citation may change.","search.full.text.search.collection.description.default":"Enter your search terms, and the computer will scan the entire collection to find where those terms appear. You can use quotation marks and other advanced search techniques to narrow your results.","search.full.text.search.collections.Description":"Search for your ancestors in birth certificates, marriage registrations, census records, and other documents.","search.full.text.search.collections.Title":"Full Text Collections","search.full.text.search.collections.resultsCount":"Results ({count}) ","search.fullTextSearch.FAQ1Answer":"FamilySearch Full-Text Search is a tool that lets you search almost 2 billion historical records that haven\'t been indexed yet. It uses AI to read and interpret text directly from document images.","search.fullTextSearch.FAQ1Question":"What does Full-Text Search do?","search.fullTextSearch.FAQ2Answer":"The list of record collections available in Full-Text Search is extensive\u2014and growing. These collections include nearly every type of historical record imaginable, from church registers and court documents to military files, newspapers, personal letters, land deeds, and more.","search.fullTextSearch.FAQ2Question":"What kinds of records can I search with FamilySearch Full-Text Search?","search.fullTextSearch.FAQ3Answer1":"The regular search looks at data that has been transcribed and indexed. In many projects,this might be just a small portion of the document\u2014often just a name and date.","search.fullTextSearch.FAQ3Answer2":"Full-Text Search, by contrast, scans the entire document. It lets you search the full sentences and paragraphs that usually go untouched in a regular indexing project.","search.fullTextSearch.FAQ3Question":"How is Full-Text Search different from the regular FamilySearch search?","search.fullTextSearch.FAQ4.TutorialName1":"August 2025 \u201cWhat is FamilySearch\u2019s Full-Text Search?\u201d","search.fullTextSearch.FAQ4.TutorialName2":"RootsTech 2025: \u201cFamilySearch Full-Text Search is Even Better!\u201d","search.fullTextSearch.FAQ4.TutorialName3":"RootsTech 2024: \u201cFull-Text Search\u201d","search.fullTextSearch.FAQ4Answer":"Yes. You can watch short video tutorials and RootsTech sessions that show how to use Full-Text Search and that highlight exciting discoveries people have made with it.","search.fullTextSearch.FAQ4Question":"Are there any tutorials or demos available?","search.fullTextSearch.FAQ5Answer":"The more recent the record, the more accurate the results. For older documents, accuracy continues to improve, but it can vary depending on handwriting style and image quality.","search.fullTextSearch.FAQ5Question":"How accurate is the AI that is reading the text?","search.fullTextSearch.FAQ6Answer":"Yes! FamilySearch encourages users to provide feedback through a dedicated community group or the feedback button within the tool itself.","search.fullTextSearch.FAQ6Question":" Can I give feedback or report issues?","search.fullTextSearch.FAQ7Answer":"You can access Full-Text Search from the Search tab on the FamilySearch homepage or directly from its landing page.","search.fullTextSearch.FAQ7Question":"How do I access FamilySearch Full-Text Search?","search.fullTextSearch.FAQHeader":"Frequently Asked Questions","search.fullTextSearch.filterOnLeftAlt":"Drawing of a filter panel on the left side of the screen with various filter options.","search.fullTextSearch.findCollections.autosuggest.helpMessage":"e.g. Alabama, Wills and Deeds, ca. 1700s-2017","search.fullTextSearch.findCollections.autosuggest.label":"Collection Title","search.fullTextSearch.findCollections.autosuggest.placeholder":"Search for a specific collection title","search.fullTextSearch.findCollections.header":"Find a Collection","search.fullTextSearch.findCollections.headerSEO":"Search for a specific collection","search.fullTextSearch.findCollections.paragraph":"Your ancestor\u2019s record belongs to a collection of similar documents. Searching a specific collection is one way to narrow your search. If you don\u2019t know the collection\u2019s exact title, start typing, and we\u2019ll try to help you.","search.fullTextSearch.findCollections.paragraphSEO":"Narrow your results by searching within a single collection of historical records. Start typing, and we\'ll suggest matching titles.","search.fullTextSearch.heading":"Full-Text Search","search.fullTextSearch.headingSEO":"Unlock new discoveries with Full-Text Search\xa0","search.fullTextSearch.howToUse.header":"How to use FamilySearch Full-Text Search","search.fullTextSearch.howToUse.step1Header":"Enter your keywords","search.fullTextSearch.howToUse.step1Subheader":"This can be a name or any other detail you think might help you find your ancestor.","search.fullTextSearch.howToUse.step2Header":"Apply filters for precision","search.fullTextSearch.howToUse.step2Subheader":"These are located on the left side of the screen, below your search terms.","search.fullTextSearch.howToUse.step3Header":"Review your results","search.fullTextSearch.howToUse.step3Subheader":"Adjust filters or keywords until you have the right balance of quality and quantity.","search.fullTextSearch.howToUse.subheader":"In most cases, a single keyword is enough to start. Then, depending on your results, add or remove words or apply filters to refine your search.","search.fullTextSearch.howToVideoBenefit1":"Gain early access to records by searching collections that haven\'t been indexed yet.","search.fullTextSearch.howToVideoBenefit2":"Not sure about your ancestor\'s name? Try a place, date, event, or other detail that might be connected to them.","search.fullTextSearch.howToVideoBenefit3":"Search every word contained in the record, including any notes.","search.fullTextSearch.howToVideoHeader":"How Full-Text Search transforms your research","search.fullTextSearch.howToVideoSubheader":"Save time while uncovering details not available to you with other searches.","search.fullTextSearch.manSearchingRecordArtAlt":"Drawing of a man searching various types of historical records.","search.fullTextSearch.metaDescription":"Search for your ancestors in birth certificates, marriage registrations, census records, and other documents.","search.fullTextSearch.metaDescriptionSEO":"Search inside historical records, newspapers, and handwritten documents\u2014even those not yet indexed\u2014with FamilySearch Full-Text Search.","search.fullTextSearch.recordHeader":"A new era in search technology","search.fullTextSearch.recordSubheader":"With handwriting recognition and Optical Character Recognition (OCR) software, we can convert an image of text into a machine-readable text format giving you the ability to search the full text of these records before they are even indexed.","search.fullTextSearch.searchFormAlt":"Drawing of a search form with various search fields.","search.fullTextSearch.searchTips.heading":"Advanced Search Tips","search.fullTextSearch.searchTips.headingSEO":"Tips for successful full-text searching","search.fullTextSearch.searchTips.subheading":"Try including the following in your searches to help narrow down your results:","search.fullTextSearch.searchTips.subheadingSEO":"Too many results? Try these strategies to focus your search:","search.fullTextSearch.socialShareDescriptionSEO":"Find new details about your ancestor in unindexed historical records.","search.fullTextSearch.socialShareTitleSEO":"Make new discoveries with Full-Text Search","search.fullTextSearch.subheader2":"Unlock hidden discoveries in historical records that have never been searchable till now. Check back often as we keep adding millions of images. More information below.","search.fullTextSearch.subheader2SEO":"Search inside unindexed historical records to uncover names, dates, and details that standard searches can\'t find.","search.fullTextSearchLandingTitle":"Full-Text Search","search.fullTextSearchLandingTitleSEO":"Make Unexpected Discoveries with FamilySearch Full-Text Search","search.gen.browseAllJiapu":"Browse All Jiapu","search.gen.collection.browseAll":"Browse All","search.gen.collection.howToUse":"How to Use This Source","search.gen.collection.title":"Genealogies: Collection Details","search.gen.exploreCollections":"Explore one of our collections","search.gen.form.validation.invalidChars":"Input cannot contain the following characters: {invalidChars}","search.gen.genDiffFromTree":"How is FamilySearch Genealogies different from FamilySearch Family Tree?","search.gen.genDiffFromTreeExplain":"Genealogies is a database of tens of thousands of personal family trees, lineages, and other histories. The FamilySearch Family Tree, by comparison, is a single tree or lineage for the entire human family.","search.gen.goToFamilyTree":"Go to the Family Tree","search.gen.highDataAccuracy":"High Data Accuracy","search.gen.moderateDataAccuracy":"Moderate Data Accuracy","search.gen.researchSubmittedBySources":"Within them you\'ll find thousands of family trees submitted by individuals and professional organizations.","search.gen.results":"Genealogies Search Results","search.gen.searchForPerson":"Search for a Person","search.gen.specificSourceBrowse":"View all trees","search.gen.specificTree":"Search for a specific tree","search.gen.specificTreeSubheading":"Let us help you find the tree you\'re looking for. Enter a surname or place associated with the family, and we\'ll search for it in all of our collections.","search.gen.submissions":"Submissions","search.gen.submissions.allColumns":"Tree Name, Collection, Person Count, and Last Updated","search.gen.submissions.audioFor":"Audio for:","search.gen.submissions.autosuggestHelp":"{submissionType} include information in their title or description that often contains the names of interviewees, first ancestors, locations, and clan names. Search for them here.","search.gen.submissions.autosuggestLabel":"Find {submissionType} by Keyword","search.gen.submissions.autosuggestPlaceholder":"Enter a surname, place, village, or clan.","search.gen.submissions.collection":"Collection","search.gen.submissions.collectionCountUpdated":"Collection, Person Count, and Last Updated","search.gen.submissions.collectionFilter":"Filter by Collection","search.gen.submissions.filter.chip.showAll":"Show All","search.gen.submissions.filterResults":"Filter Results ({resultCount, number})","search.gen.submissions.keywordSearch":"Keyword Search","search.gen.submissions.lastUpdated":"Last Updated","search.gen.submissions.pageDescription":"A searchable list of submissions within the FamilySearch genealogies database.","search.gen.submissions.pageTitle":"Genealogies - Submission List","search.gen.submissions.personCount":"Person Count","search.gen.submissions.resetSearch":"Reset Search","search.gen.submissions.seeAllResults":"See All Results","search.gen.submissions.treeName":"Tree Name","search.gen.title":"Free Family Trees","search.gen.unknownDataAccuracy":"Unknown Data Accuracy","search.gen.uploadTree":"Upload your individual tree","search.gen.viewAllTrees":"View all trees in this collection","search.genDetails.closeCollectionDetail":"Close Collection Details","search.genDetails.searchThisSubmission":"Search This Submission","search.genDetails.showMoreDetail":"Show More Detail","search.genDetails.submissionId":"Submission ID","search.genDetails.submissionSources":"Submission Sources","search.genDetails.submittedBy":"Submitted by: <contributorLink>{contributorName}</contributorLink>","search.genealogies":"Genealogies","search.genealogies.metaDescription":"Search for your ancestors in genealogies, jiapu and histories submitted by other people, societies and organizations.","search.genealogies.subheader2":"FamilySearch Genealogies is a large directory of family trees, also known as lineages or pedigrees, that people and organizations have shared with FamilySearch. We organize the information into collections and make it available for you to search.","search.hr.collection.title":"Records: Collection Details","search.hr.person.F":"Female","search.hr.person.M":"Male","search.hr.person.U":"Unknown","search.hr.person.altNames":"Alternate Names","search.hr.person.citation":"Citing This Record","search.hr.person.others":"Other People on This Record","search.hr.person.sex":"Sex","search.location.browsePlacesDescription":"Different regions of the world call for different research strategies. Select a place, and we\u2019ll show you the tools and resources we have to help you discover your ancestors who lived there.","search.location.courseCount":"{total, plural, =0 {There are no courses available for} one {We have # learning course to help you do your family history research in} other {We have # learning courses to help you do your family history research in}}","search.location.courseCount.Chinese":"{total, plural, =0 {Chinese Genealogy Research Pages Coming Soon!} one {We have # learning course to help you do your family history research in} other {We have # learning courses to help you do your family history research in}}","search.location.errorHeader":"Something Went Wrong","search.location.errorMessage":"We can help you search literally billions of records, but something isn\u2019t working correctly right now.\\n\\nYou can always try this again later.","search.location.findAPlace":"Find a Country, Province, or State","search.location.gettingStarted":"Getting Started","search.location.guangdongVillageFinder.header":"Guangdong Village Finder","search.location.learningCenter.header":"Learning Center","search.location.learningCenter.playIconAltText":"Play Icon","search.location.learningCenter.seeAllCourses":"See all {cleanedPlace} Learning Courses","search.location.metaDescription":"Different regions of the world call for different research strategies. Find free resources to 