tHeader":"Collection, Person Count","search.locationPage.genealogiesTableHead":"Name, Collection, Person Count","search.locationPage.getInvolved.heading":"Get Involved Projects","search.locationPage.historicalRecords":"Indexed Historical Records","search.locationPage.historicalRecordsCard.birth":"Birth","search.locationPage.historicalRecordsCard.death":"Death","search.locationPage.historicalRecordsCard.marriage":"Marriage","search.locationPage.imageOnlyHeader":"Image-Only Historical Records","search.locationPage.imageTableHead":"Name, Images","search.locationPage.images":"Images","search.locationPage.indexedTableHead":"Name, Records","search.locationPage.metaDescription":"Search and explore historical record collections and more in {region}, {subRegion}","search.locationPage.noCatalogItems":"No catalog items found.","search.locationPage.noCollectionsFound":"No collections found.","search.locationPage.noTitle":"[No Title]","search.locationPage.pageTitle":"Family History Research in {region}, {subRegion}","search.locationPage.recordType":"Record Type","search.locationPage.records":"Records","search.locationPage.seeAllCatalogMaterial":"See all {subRegion} Catalog Material","search.locationPage.seeAllCollections":"See all {subRegion} Collections","search.locationPage.seeAllGenealogies":"See all {subRegion} Genealogies","search.locationPage.seeAllImageCollections":"See all {subRegion} Image Collections","search.locationPage.showingNumCatalog":"Showing {count} of {total} Catalog Records for {subRegion}","search.locationPage.showingNumCollections":"Showing {count} of {total} Collections for {subRegion}","search.locationPage.showingNumGenealogies":"Showing {count} of {total} Genealogies for {subRegion}","search.locationPage.showingNumImageOnly":"Showing {count} of {total} Collections for {subRegion}","search.locationPage.subHeading":"Welcome to our {subRegion} research page. We\'ve brought together tools to help you with your research in {subRegion}.","search.locationPage.wiki.guidedLink":"Guided Research for {place}","search.locationPage.wiki.link":"View Wiki for {place}","search.mormonGen.collectionsHeading":"Collections","search.mormonGen.heading":"MORMON<sup>\u2122</sup><br/>Genealogical Research","search.mormonGen.pageDescription":"Searchable genealogy records from Utah and around the world from 1836 to the mid-1900s are available below. Records include mission calls, membership, migration and pioneer travel databases, military service, and biographical sources.","search.mormonGen.pageTitle":"MORMON\u2122 Genealogical Research","search.notFound.body":"Sometimes in life, less is more. Try your search again with a little less information. If you get too many results, you can always add more later.","search.notFound.optionReload":"Reload the Page","search.records":"Search Historical Records","search.records.browseCollections":"Browse All Collections","search.records.browsePlaces":"Browse Places","search.records.collectionFieldTitle":"Collection Title","search.records.collectionHeader":"Find a Collection","search.records.collectionImageAlt":"Link to page for browsing all collections.","search.records.collectionSubheader":"Your ancestor\u2019s record belongs to a collection of similar documents\u2014Argentina Baptisms, for example, or United States Census, 1940. Searching a specific collection is one way to narrow your search. If you don\'t know the collection\'s exact title, start typing, and we\'ll try to help you.","search.records.familyHeader":"How do historical records help me learn about my family?","search.records.familySubheader":"Historical records can often reveal important details about where your family lived or came from, when family members were born or got married, and when they died.","search.records.helpArticleLink":"Tips for Effective Searches","search.records.locationFieldError":"Something went wrong. Try again later.","search.records.locationFieldTitle":"Find a Country, Province, or State","search.records.locationHeader":"Search by Place","search.records.locationImageAlt":"Drawing of two people searching for historical records in different areas of the world.","search.records.locationSubheader":"Different regions of the world call for different research strategies. Enter a place, and we\'ll show you the tools and resources we have to help you discover your ancestors who lived there.","search.records.metaDescription":"Search for your ancestors in birth certificates, marriage registrations, census records, and other documents.","search.records.recordHeader":"What is a historical record?","search.records.recordSubheader":"A historical record is an official document that recognizes an event in a person\'s life. Examples include marriage licenses, draft cards, birth certificates, and census records.","search.records.subheader2":"Records create a paper trail for your ancestors and can lead you to important details about their life. Enter a name, and we\'ll look for it in birth certificates, marriage registrations, census records, and other official documents.","search.records.whatIsARecordImageAlt":"Drawing of a man searching various types of historical records.","search.records.worldImageAlt":"Link to page for browsing all places.","search.results.error.body":"Unfortunately, something went wrong, and we are unable to display the search results. Try refreshing the page, or come back later.","search.searchBanner.notice":"Important Notice","search.simpleSearch.formHeading":"Search Records","search.simpleSearch.heading":"Simple Search","search.simpleSearch.results":"Simple Search Results","search.simpleSearch.subheader":"Find crucial information buried in millions of difficult-to-read handwriting or records that were not previously indexed. Try a new way to search our full-text historical records.","search.sourcelinker.addNewFact":"Add New Fact: {factType}","search.sourcelinker.addNewPerson":"Add New Person: {leftPersonName}","search.sourcelinker.attachedIconLabel":"Person is Attached